    <p style="font-size:0.82rem;color:#78716c;margin-top:2rem;">Also selling in: <a href="/suburbs/karana-downs" style="color:#b98229;">Karana Downs</a>, <a href="/suburbs/anstead" style="color:#b98229;">Anstead</a>, <a href="/suburbs/bellbowrie" style="color:#b98229;">Bellbowrie</a>.</p>
